  {
    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "So if I sum up:\r\n - this icon can be confusing (@vvo didn't get the meaning of this icon)\r\n - icons are better, especially for such icons. But needs to be easily recognizable\r\n - if something is more universal than the other, let's choose the more universal\r\n\r\n@auareyoualgolia do you have another proposal of icon that would be more universal?",
